window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I was once a mighty Paladin of Darkness, mother of all the Elements. The one and only of my kind.<br> <br> Some called me the chosen one, a savior destined to rescue the world; others insisted I would be its downfall.<br> <br> I never got the chance to discover who was right. Society conspired with the traitors to trap me in the deadly Element of Time.<br> <br> But a year later, I managed to break free . . . wait, how has it been 700 years?</p>"; 
